# 🌀 AnimeManager Console App (.NET 8 + EF Core)

A simple console-based CRUD application built with **.NET 8**, **Entity Framework Core**, and **SQLite**. It manages a list of anime characters with details such as name, anime, power level, and famous quotes.

---

## 📦 Project Structure

- `Models/AnimeCharacter.cs` – Entity model class.
- `Data/AppdbContext.cs` – EF Core DB context for SQLite.
- `Services/AnimeCharacterService.cs` – Handles CRUD logic.
- `Program.cs` – Application entry point.
- `animecharacters.db` – SQLite database (auto-created).

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add anime characters
- ✅ Retrieve all characters from database
- ✅ Auto-initializes database using `EnsureCreated()`
- ✅ Handles primary key auto-increment
- ✅ Logs common errors like missing DB fields

---

## ⚙️ Technologies

- [.NET 8](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/download)
- [Entity Framework Core](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/ef/core/)
- SQLite (local database)

